<template>
    <v-app-bar app>
      <v-app-bar-nav-icon @click="drawer = !drawer" class="d-md-none"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>
  
      <v-toolbar-title>My Store</v-toolbar-title>
  
      <v-spacer></v-spacer>
  
      <!-- Desktop buttons -->
      <v-btn text class="d-none d-md-flex" to="/home">Home</v-btn>
      <v-btn text class="d-none d-md-flex" to="/shop">Shop</v-btn>
      <v-btn text class="d-none d-md-flex" to="/blog">Blog</v-btn>
      <v-btn text class="d-none d-md-flex" to="/cart">Cart</v-btn>
  
      <!-- Mobile menu -->
      <v-navigation-drawer
        v-model="drawer"
        app
        :temporary="true"
        :clipped="$vuetify.breakpoint.mdAndUp"
      >
        <v-list>
          <v-list-item v-for="item in items" :key="item.value" :to="{ path: '/' + item.value }" router>
            <v-list-item-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-item-title>
          </v-list-item>
        </v-list>
      </v-navigation-drawer>
    </v-app-bar>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    name: 'NavbarComponent',
    data() {
      return {
        drawer: false,
        items: [
          { title: 'Home', value: 'home' },
          { title: 'Shop', value: 'shop' },
          { title: 'Blog', value: 'blog' },
          { title: 'Cart', value: 'cart' },
        ],
      };
    },
  };
  </script>
  
  <style scoped>
  .v-app-bar {
    padding: 0;
  }
  </style>
